(Adrax and Autofire are LONG gone from the Predacon base, your shots are 
wasted.  Sorry.  Code, the ion disk is designed to penetrate enemy armor and 
go all the way through out the other side.  Let's just say the energy cuts 
through the rock, and misses Land Mine's left temple by two millimeters, 
also, everyone, Mosquitor is unconscious, in stasis lock, and possibly 
decapitated)

Injector/Manterror/Bumblebee/Double Punch:



Injector laughed, firing off two stinger missiles down at the rock Megatron, 
KitKat, and Land Mine were behind, followed by a single optic blast.

---

Manterror fired off two ion disks at Time Bomb.

---

Double Punch deactivated his cloaking device, deciding it would just cause 
confusion and may result in him being shot by his team.  Raising both 
pinchers, he fired off a missile, the missile passing Time Bomb, striking a 
tree.

---

Injector cursed, going full speed, after a minute he turned, the side all the 
other Predacons were on behind the rock, was exposed to him!

Raising both stinger missile launchers, he fired two stinger missiles at 
Megatron, and two at Land Mine.
